Package: vcfR
Title: Tools for Working with Variant Call Format ('VCF') Files
Description: Tools for working with variant call format ('VCF') files. Reads in
    'VCF', 'GFF' and 'FASTA' data for visualization. Includes tools for filtering
    and writing to 'VCF' files.
Version: 1.1.0
